    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the bacon is cooking, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pot with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
